{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/frontend/apple-clone/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ziglog","author":"zigsong","lang":"en"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"7c0f0293-e473-5bc3-a6b6-9e450a6edd8d","excerpt":"새로 알게된 CSS 속성들 우테코 Lv4 마크업 미션으로 애플 클론코딩을 진행했다. 14일 화요일에 미션이 주어졌는데, 제출일은 16일 아침까지고, 한국 시간 15일 새벽…","html":"<p>새로 알게된 CSS 속성들</p>\n<!-- more -->\n<p>우테코 Lv4 마크업 미션으로 애플 클론코딩을 진행했다. 14일 화요일에 미션이 주어졌는데, 제출일은 16일 아침까지고, 한국 시간 15일 새벽 2시에 애플 신제품 발표로 홈페이지가 리뉴얼되면서 (ㅎ) 알면서도 곤혹을 치뤘다. 또 모든 크루들이 그랬겠지만, 17일에 있었던 데모데이 준비까지 겹쳐 이틀 밤을 거의 새다시피 하고 몸이 엉망진창이…</p>\n<p>일부 섹션을 생략한 완성작은 <a href=\"https://zigsong.github.io/html-apple-store/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">여기</a>에…</p>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/bcc55880879119ec54e30d60b09a609b/5c953/01.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.75675675675676%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"01\" title=\"01\" src=\"/static/bcc55880879119ec54e30d60b09a609b/fcda8/01.png\" srcset=\"/static/bcc55880879119ec54e30d60b09a609b/12f09/01.png 148w,\n/static/bcc55880879119ec54e30d60b09a609b/e4a3f/01.png 295w,\n/static/bcc55880879119ec54e30d60b09a609b/fcda8/01.png 590w,\n/static/bcc55880879119ec54e30d60b09a609b/efc66/01.png 885w,\n/static/bcc55880879119ec54e30d60b09a609b/c83ae/01.png 1180w,\n/static/bcc55880879119ec54e30d60b09a609b/5c953/01.png 3540w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<h2 id=\"html-tags\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#html-tags\" aria-label=\"html tags permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HTML tags</h2>\n<h3 id=\"aside\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#aside\" aria-label=\"aside permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;aside></code></h3>\n<p>문서의 주요 내용과 간접적으로만 연관된 부분을 나타낼 때 사용한다. 주로 사이드바 혹은 콜아웃 박스로 표현한다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"article-vs-section\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#article-vs-section\" aria-label=\"article vs section permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;article></code> vs <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;section></code></h3>\n<p><strong>article</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>블로그 포스트, 신문 기사 등 하나하나를 가리킨다.</li>\n<li>자체만으로 독립적으로 다른 페이지에 보여져도 문제가 없을 때 사용한다.\n<ul>\n<li>main과 상관 없는 독립적인 정보를 제공한다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>section</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>연관 있는 내용들을 하나로 묶어줄 때 사용한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"img--vs-background-image\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#img--vs-background-image\" aria-label=\"img  vs background image permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;img /></code> vs <code class=\"language-text\">background-image</code></h3>\n<p>많은 경우 습관적으로 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;img /></code> 태그를 사용하는데, 아래의 상황들에서는 <code class=\"language-text\">background-image</code>를 사용하는 것이 바람직하다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>문서의 내용과는 별개로, 스타일 목적으로 사용되는 경우</li>\n<li>이미지가 없어도 문서를 읽는 데 지장이 없는 경우</li>\n</ul>\n<p>실제로 애플 공홈에서도 각 섹션별 이미지를 <code class=\"language-text\">background-image</code> 속성으로 설정하고 있었다. (그새 홈페이지가 또 바뀌었다..)</p>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/3df8be0d12bb4ec2d8d0458ef3b3a4f6/6e29b/02.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 42.567567567567565%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"02\" title=\"02\" src=\"/static/3df8be0d12bb4ec2d8d0458ef3b3a4f6/fcda8/02.png\" srcset=\"/static/3df8be0d12bb4ec2d8d0458ef3b3a4f6/12f09/02.png 148w,\n/static/3df8be0d12bb4ec2d8d0458ef3b3a4f6/e4a3f/02.png 295w,\n/static/3df8be0d12bb4ec2d8d0458ef3b3a4f6/fcda8/02.png 590w,\n/static/3df8be0d12bb4ec2d8d0458ef3b3a4f6/efc66/02.png 885w,\n/static/3df8be0d12bb4ec2d8d0458ef3b3a4f6/c83ae/02.png 1180w,\n/static/3df8be0d12bb4ec2d8d0458ef3b3a4f6/6e29b/02.png 1610w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<p><strong>Ref</strong>\n<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T7h8O7dpJIg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T7h8O7dpJIg</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"css-attributes\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#css-attributes\" aria-label=\"css attributes permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS attributes</h2>\n<h3 id=\"background-position\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#background-position\" aria-label=\"background position permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>background-position</h3>\n<p>말 그대로 배경 이미지의 위치를 정하는 속성으로, x/y축을 통해 가로와 세로 위치를 정할 수 있다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"float\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#float\" aria-label=\"float permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>float</h3>\n<p>요소가 일반적인 흐름을 벗어나 어디에 ‘뜰’ 것인지를 정하는 속성이다. 웹 개발을 배우기 시작했을 때 접했는데, 거의(사실 한 번도) 사용하지 않고 있었다. 문서 흐름의 좌측이나 우측으로 배치되며 메인 콘텐츠의 흐름을 벗어나 사용한다. 애플 홈페이지에서는 footer의 일부 텍스트에 포함되어 있었다. 의미를 고려했을 때 유용하게 사용해볼 수 있을 것 같다.</p>\n<p><strong>&#x3C;footer의 locale 정보만 우측으로 치우친 경우></strong>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/9def8a9d626a0b2e4b175eef596c093b/fe9e8/03.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 46.621621621621614%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"03\" title=\"03\" src=\"/static/9def8a9d626a0b2e4b175eef596c093b/fcda8/03.png\" srcset=\"/static/9def8a9d626a0b2e4b175eef596c093b/12f09/03.png 148w,\n/static/9def8a9d626a0b2e4b175eef596c093b/e4a3f/03.png 295w,\n/static/9def8a9d626a0b2e4b175eef596c093b/fcda8/03.png 590w,\n/static/9def8a9d626a0b2e4b175eef596c093b/efc66/03.png 885w,\n/static/9def8a9d626a0b2e4b175eef596c093b/fe9e8/03.png 1146w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>👾 <code class=\"language-text\">clear</code> 속성에 대해서도 알아보자!</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"margin-vs-padding\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#margin-vs-padding\" aria-label=\"margin vs padding permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>margin vs padding</h3>\n<p>각각 요소의 바깥 영역, 요소를 포함하는 영역이라는 차이는 당연히 알고 있다. 그러나 애플 공홈에서 너무나 제멋대로(?) 쓰고 있는 것을 보니, 역시 단지 취향 차이일 뿐일까? 🤔</p>\n<h3 id=\"will-change\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#will-change\" aria-label=\"will change permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>will-change</h3>\n<p>요소에 예상되는 변화의 종류에 관한 힌트를 브라우저에 제공한다. 실제 요소가 변화되기 전에 미리 브라우저는 적절하게 최적화할 수 있어, 성능 비용이 큰 작업을 미리 실행함으로써 페이지의 반응성을 증가시킬 수 있다. will-change를 사용하면 해당 레이어는 GPU에 업로드되어 처리된다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>👾 will-change에 묶인 최적화는 몇몇 많은 자원을 소모할 수 있으므로, 꼭 필요한 경우에만 사용하도록 한다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"transform-matrix\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#transform-matrix\" aria-label=\"transform matrix permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>transform: matrix</h3>\n<p>원근감(perspective)을 제외한 나머지 스타일을 일괄 적용시킬 수 있는 메소드로, 무려 6개의 값을 전달받는다.</p>\n\n          <div class=\"gatsby-remark-prismjs-copy-button-container\">\n            <div class=\"gatsby-remark-prismjs-copy-button\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" onclick=\"gatsbyRemarkCopyToClipboard(this, this.parentNode.nextElementSibling)\">\n              Copy\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">matrix (scaleX, skewX, skewY, scaleY, translateX, translateY)</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"text-shadow\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#text-shadow\" aria-label=\"text shadow permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>text-shadow</h3>\n<p>글자에 그림자 효과를 주는 속성으로, <code class=\"language-text\">font-weight</code> hover 시 transition이 먹지 않아 대신 사용하게 되었다. <code class=\"language-text\">text-shadow</code>를 잘 활용하여 <code class=\"language-text\">font-weight</code>보다 편한 텍스트를 구현할 수 있을 것 같다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"font-smoothing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#font-smoothing\" aria-label=\"font smoothing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>font-smoothing</h3>\n\n          <div class=\"gatsby-remark-prismjs-copy-button-container\">\n            <div class=\"gatsby-remark-prismjs-copy-button\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" onclick=\"gatsbyRemarkCopyToClipboard(this, this.parentNode.nextElementSibling)\">\n              Copy\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">body {\n  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>Webkit 기반의 Safari 및 Mac 등에서 완벽히 구현되며 이 외에는 제한적으로 사용된다고 한다. CRA의 기본 스타일로도 지정되어 있다고!</p>\n<h3 id=\"flex-direction-row-reverse\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#flex-direction-row-reverse\" aria-label=\"flex direction row reverse permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>flex-direction: row-reverse</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">reverse</code>를 쓸 바에는 그냥 좌측에 와야 할 요소를 코드 상으로 먼저 적으면 되는 거 아닌가? 생각했었다. 그런데 아래와 같이 이미지와 텍스트가 좌우 배치되어있지만 웹 접근성을 고려했을 때 텍스트가 먼저 읽혀야 하는 경우(특히나 다른 섹션들은 텍스트가 이미지보다 좌측에 등장하여 일관성 유지가 필요하다.) <code class=\"language-text\">row-reverse</code> 값을 사용해야 한다는 것을 깨달았다.</p>\n<p><strong>&#x3C;이미지와 텍스트가 보여지는 순서와 의미상 순서가 일치하지 않는 경우></strong>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/deeb5aa33cd09d8b4493ba63c1660298/2f8cb/04.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 58.10810810810811%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"04\" title=\"04\" src=\"/static/deeb5aa33cd09d8b4493ba63c1660298/fcda8/04.png\" srcset=\"/static/deeb5aa33cd09d8b4493ba63c1660298/12f09/04.png 148w,\n/static/deeb5aa33cd09d8b4493ba63c1660298/e4a3f/04.png 295w,\n/static/deeb5aa33cd09d8b4493ba63c1660298/fcda8/04.png 590w,\n/static/deeb5aa33cd09d8b4493ba63c1660298/efc66/04.png 885w,\n/static/deeb5aa33cd09d8b4493ba63c1660298/c83ae/04.png 1180w,\n/static/deeb5aa33cd09d8b4493ba63c1660298/2f8cb/04.png 1689w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong>Ref</strong>\n<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/background-position\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/background-position</a>\n<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/CSS/float\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/CSS/float</a>\n<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/CSS/will-change\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/CSS/will-change</a>\n<a href=\"https://wit.nts-corp.com/2017/06/05/4571\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://wit.nts-corp.com/2017/06/05/4571</a>\n<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/CSS/transform-function/matrix()\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/CSS/transform-function/matrix()</a>\n<a href=\"https://rgy0409.tistory.com/2990\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://rgy0409.tistory.com/2990</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tips\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tips\" aria-label=\"tips permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tips</h2>\n<h3 id=\"css-variables\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#css-variables\" aria-label=\"css variables permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>css variables</h3>\n<p>사용자 지정 속성을 사용하여 문서 전반에서 재활용할 수 있는 값들을 변수로 미리 등록해둘 수 있다. 두 개의 대쉬(<code class=\"language-text\">--</code>)로 시작하는 변수명으로 짓는 것이 일반적이다.</p>\n\n          <div class=\"gatsby-remark-prismjs-copy-button-container\">\n            <div class=\"gatsby-remark-prismjs-copy-button\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" onclick=\"gatsbyRemarkCopyToClipboard(this, this.parentNode.nextElementSibling)\">\n              Copy\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">element</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">--main-bg-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> brown<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">:root</code> psuedo class를 사용하여 HTML 문서 어디에서나 접근할 수 있는 속성을 정의할 수도 있다.</p>\n\n          <div class=\"gatsby-remark-prismjs-copy-button-container\">\n            <div class=\"gatsby-remark-prismjs-copy-button\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" onclick=\"gatsbyRemarkCopyToClipboard(this, this.parentNode.nextElementSibling)\">\n              Copy\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">:root</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">--main-bg-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> brown<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>사용은 아래처럼 <code class=\"language-text\">var</code> 키워드를 사용한다!</p>\n\n          <div class=\"gatsby-remark-prismjs-copy-button-container\">\n            <div class=\"gatsby-remark-prismjs-copy-button\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" onclick=\"gatsbyRemarkCopyToClipboard(this, this.parentNode.nextElementSibling)\">\n              Copy\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">body</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--main-bg-color<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"font-src-local\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#font-src-local\" aria-label=\"font src local permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>font src local</h3>\n\n          <div class=\"gatsby-remark-prismjs-copy-button-container\">\n            <div class=\"gatsby-remark-prismjs-copy-button\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" onclick=\"gatsbyRemarkCopyToClipboard(this, this.parentNode.nextElementSibling)\">\n              Copy\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@font-face</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"SF Pro Text\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> normal<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 300<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">src</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">local</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"🍎\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string url\">\"../fonts/sf-pro-display_thin.woff2\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"woff2\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></p